@startuml
title UC-FR-08 Module Enrollment Management
left to right direction

actor "Staff (Authorized)" as Staff

rectangle "Academic Management System" {
  (Enroll Student in Module) as Enroll
  (Validate Module Enrollment Rules) as Validate
  (Reject Module Enrollment) as Reject
}

Staff -- Enroll
Enroll ..> Validate : <<include>>
Reject ..> Enroll : <<extend>>

note top of Validate
Rules include:
- student exists
- module exists
- active course enrollment exists
- module belongs to enrolled course
- no duplicate enrollment for term
end note

@enduml
